Text: it is indeed a great movie

Peripou sti mesi, ekei pou o diefthintis tis filakis pazarevei tin misthosi tov kratoumenon, to "real player" deixnei flou. Amesos meta to flou epanerxetai me elaxisti entasi ixou.

Oi ypotitloi exoun kommenous kapoious dialogous.

Tha elega oti einai kako video, an kai telika mporesa na to parakolouthiso. Isos epeidi to eixa dei sto sinema.
